as principal admin password "admin" do
set x = "hello"
set y = split(x,"..")
set z = concat(x,y.fst)
return { x=x, y=y.snd, z=z }

as principal admin password "admin" do
set x = "HELLO"
set y = split(x,"")
set z = split(x,".....X")
set x1 = concat(z.fst,z.snd)
set x2 = concat(y.fst,y.snd)
set x3 = tolower(x)
set records = []
append to records with y
append to records with z 
append to records with x1
append to records with x2
append to records with x3
return records
